data.description: Welcome home!  This well cared for 2/3 bedroom 2 bath home located in a premier waterfront community is waiting for you.  The oversized lot with large shed/garage gives you all the room you need for outdoor living or additional building with county approval.  Across the street from the park makes it easy to get outdoors and move.  The home has new roof, fresh paint and new carpet.  Ready to move in! Convenient to restaurants, shopping and work.  This home is a DREAM, make it your own!
